{"title":"HyperLogLogAndBitMap","uid":"62b40b7a4c4e7564b743dce35ade9e59","slug":"HyperLogLogAndBitMap","date":"2021-10-12T15:53:57.000Z","updated":"2021-10-12T16:08:29.518Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HyperLogLogAndBitMap.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"Redis高级数据结构-HyperLogLog-和-Bitmap\"><a href=\"#Redis高级数据结构-HyperLogLog-和-Bitmap\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Redis高级数据结构 HyperLogLog 和 Bitmap\"></a>Redis高级数据结构 HyperLogLog 和 Bitmap</h2><h3 id=\"HyperLogLog\"><a href=\"#HyperLogLog\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HyperLogLog\"></a>HyperLogLog</h3><ol>\n<li><p>采用一种基数算法，完成对独立数据的统计</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>占用空间小，无论数据有多少，只占有12K的空间</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>它是一种不精确的算法，标准误差为 0.81%</p>\n<h4 id=\"基本使用\"><a href=\"#基本使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本使用\"></a>基本使用</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 统计20万个重复数据的独立总数.</span>\n  <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Test</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">testHyperLogLog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n      <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> redisKey <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"test:hll:01\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   \n      <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n   